---
---

<section id="about" class="section-spacing section-padding relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-96 h-96 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full opacity-10"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--color-accent-blue), transparent 60%); filter: blur(100px);">
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Visual -->
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-square max-w-md mx-auto rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"
            style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0a0a14 0%, #12081e 50%, #081420 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);">
            <div class="p-12 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-overlay opacity-40"></div>

              <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-8 flex items-center justify-center"
                  style="background: var(--gradient-primary);">
                  <span class="text-white font-extrabold text-4xl">E</span>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">Erronatus</h3>

                <p class="text-sm font-mono" style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan);">
                  // AI Automation, Systematized
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-2xl opacity-12 -z-10"
            style="background: var(--gradient-secondary); filter: blur(60px);">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Copy -->
      <div class="reveal-right">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase" style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan);">
          The Mission
        </span>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-4 mb-10">
          AI Automation
          <br />
          <span class="gradient-text">For Everyone</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Erronatus was built by someone who got tired of scattered tutorials and
            half-documented tools. Every guide was missing something. Every YouTube video
            skipped the hard parts. Every GitHub repo assumed you already knew everything.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            So we built the system we wished existed — every configuration file, every API
            integration, every automation workflow, documented and tested. Not theory scraped
            from documentation. A working system, deployed and running, turned into a guide
            anyone can follow.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            The Erronatus Blueprint is the result. Three tiers for three levels of ambition.
            Whether you want a personal AI assistant or a fully autonomous business
            operation, the complete playbook is here.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {[
            { value: '14+', label: 'APIs Integrated' },
            { value: '5', label: 'AI Engines' },
            { value: '24', label: 'Chapters' },
          ].map(stat => (
            <div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold gradient-text">{stat.value}</div>
              <div class="text-xs mt-1.5" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">{stat.label}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
